Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:33.22,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}嵐の後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:36.25,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}透き通る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:39.30,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}光の粒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:47.24,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}混じり気のない思い　残るの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:49.69,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}二人でいると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:51.88,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}胸が熱いね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:56.94,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}嘘の付けない君が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:59.33,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}夢が破れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:01.58,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}泡になっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:05.73,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}後悔しない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.40,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}想一直注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.54,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}要一直注视着哟
