Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:26.55,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}被旋风扰动心神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:29.73,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}越上云端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:33.22,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}暴风雨之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:36.25,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}清澈而明净
